ğŸš€ Conclusion

This project demonstrates how data analytics can support global health strategies by identifying nutrition risks and disparities.
It highlights the paradoxical relationship between overnutrition and undernutrition and shows how Python, SQL, and visualization tools can transform public health data into meaningful insights.

